Title: Run, No. 17! Piccolo's Suicidal Resistance
Actors: Masako Nozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Hiromi Tsuru
Plot: Cell's arrival forces Piccolo and the Androids into an uneasy - and temporary - alliance. While the Super Namekian mounts a desperate, final attack, Goku and Gohan wait for Vegeta to emerge from the Room of Spirit and Time!
